      <h2>Who We Are</h2>
      <p>Auto Glass Victorville is a locally focused auto glass service dedicated to the High Desert communities of Victorville, Hesperia, Apple Valley, Adelanto, and Oak Hills. We specialize in one thing: getting your auto glass fixed fast, done right, and priced fair.</p>

      <h2>What We Do</h2>
      <p>From a small stone chip to a full windshield replacement, we handle every auto glass need:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Windshield repair and replacement</li>
        <li>Side and rear window replacement</li>
        <li>Side mirror repair</li>
        <li>Sunroof repair</li>
        <li>Mobile service throughout the High Desert</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Why the High Desert Trusts Us</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Local knowledge:</strong> We know how High Desert temperature swings and highway debris affect your glass — and how to fix it right.</li>
        <li><strong>Same-day service:</strong> Damaged glass is a safety issue. We move fast.</li>
        <li><strong>Mobile units:</strong> We come to your home or workplace at no extra charge.</li>
        <li><strong>Insurance friendly:</strong> We handle claims paperwork with all major insurers.</li>
        <li><strong>Warranty backed:</strong> Our workmanship comes with a lifetime warranty.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Our Commitment to Safety</h2>
      <p>Your windshield is a structural safety component — it supports the roof in a rollover and provides the backstop for passenger airbag deployment. That's why we use automotive-grade adhesives, follow proper cure times, and never cut corners on installation. Safe today, safe for the life of your vehicle.</p>

